---
title: HelloHero: Cheesy Caribbean Chicken Tacos with Tomato-Corn Salsa & Garlic Aioli
description: You told us you loved Caribbean jerk chicken, and we listened! We're giving it a spin in tasty tacos with a tangy tomato and corn salsa and crunchy salad to bring the meal together.

